324
00:14:56,420 --> 00:14:57,200
Sorry.

325
00:14:58,300 --> 00:14:59,500
I'm a police officer.

326
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:01,380
Because of

327
00:15:01,380 --> 00:15:02,610
my work,

328
