331
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:26,970
Du Cheng, right?

332
00:15:27,220 --> 00:15:28,020
I'm Xiao Shan.

333
00:15:28,570 --> 00:15:29,770
Sorry for being late.

334
00:15:30,050 --> 00:15:31,050
You must've been waiting for long.

335
00:15:31,050 --> 00:15:32,120
It's okay, I

336
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:33,760
just arrived.

337
