466
00:20:59,380 --> 00:21:01,240
I guess you're not directing at me

467
00:21:01,420 --> 00:21:01,900
but

468
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:03,830
at my position as a police officer.

469
00:21:08,340 --> 00:21:09,610
