470
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:11,200
However, no one

471
00:21:11,620 --> 00:21:12,540
but you

472
00:21:12,540 --> 00:21:13,400
can help me now.

473
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:37,530
What is this?

474
00:21:37,860 --> 00:21:39,340
There is a Xinshan Art Garden that just opened.

475
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:40,340
Did you know that?

476
00:21:42,100 --> 00:21:43,170
An exhibition

477
00:21:43,170 --> 00:21:44,570
was held there recently.

478
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:45,890
It was an exhibition of art

479
00:21:45,890 --> 00:21:47,690
by the top photographer, Mandy.

480
00:21:48,300 --> 00:21:49,330
I fought for the opportunity

481
00:21:49,330 --> 00:21:50,810
