487
00:22:06,420 --> 00:22:07,480
When did it happen?

488
00:22:08,020 --> 00:22:09,490
Evening three days ago.

489
00:22:09,940 --> 00:22:12,140
The exhibition has been called off now.

490
00:22:13,460 --> 00:22:14,660
