00:22:51,940 --> 00:22:52,920
No real damage

506
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:54,120
is caused yet.

507
00:22:54,860 --> 00:22:56,660
But if you can't find the person,

508
00:22:56,700 --> 00:22:57,610
it is likely to turn into

509
00:22:57,610 --> 00:22:59,250
